    (uuid a0000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000000d2)
  )

  (text "DK interface reservation: shared SPI + five CS_N + five INT1. Exact DK connector/header, MCU pins, voltage domain, solder bridges, and conflicts remain TBD." (at 15 60 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid a0000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000000d3)
  )

  (text "Finger connector pin order is a logical draft only: 1 GND, 2 +3V3_IMU_TBD, 3 GND, 4 SCK, 5 MOSI, 6 MISO, 7 CS_N, 8 INT1, 9 INT2_TBD." (at 120 82 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid a0000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000000d4)
  )

  (text "Each remote finger module is provisional ISM330DHCX. The separate sensor PCB is not part of this central adapter schematic." (at 120 90 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid a0000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000000d5)
  )

  (text "Reference-design lesson retained: local IMU VDD/VDDIO decoupling and short return paths are required; exact values and implementation require current datasheet review." (at 120 96 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid a0000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000000d6)
  )

  (text "SHARED SPI HARNESS DRAFT: reserve source-series damping options on SCK/MOSI and per-branch review; values/footprints TBD after cable measurements." (at 120 166 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid a0000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000000d7)
  )

  (text "INT2 is reserved at each logical finger interface but is not mapped to the DK in this draft." (at 120 173 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left bottom))
    (uuid a0000000-0000-4000-8000-0000000000d8)
  )

  (text "POWER PLACEHOLDER" (at 15 205 0)
